data.description: Come and check out this exceptional townhome at  'Legends of the Casades!'  This 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home nestled into the hillside in Rancho Cascades, is conveniently located to close to the convergence of the  5, 210, 405, and 14 freeways.  The rolling hills surrounding this area, offer a welcome respite from the hustle and bustle of the valley.  Step in from the welcoming courtyard to the open floorplan.  The great room, opens to a large kitchen with ample counterspace and storage.  Easy entertaining as it opens into the living room and private patio with grassy area looking out to the hillside.  3 spacious bedrooms upstairs, where in the master suite you can soak your troubles away in the luxurious tub, separate from the walk in shower in the master bathroom.   The HOA community offers a pool and spa with mountain views, hiking trails and children's play area, to make this the perfect retreat for the whole family.  This home has been virtually staged.
